name: Oversized Chunky Jumper
description:
Cover up in style with preppy and slouchy knitwear.

A cool boyfriend cardigan or sweet jumper is the perfect way to cover up when it gets a little chilly. Striped knitwear is gorgeous for creating this season’s preppy styling, and keep an eye out for quirky prints like crosses and hearts for an on- trend look. Capture the vintage trend seen on the catwalks with crochet in warm colours like rust, yellow and tan.

Shape- wise, slouchy, oversized knits are big news, or choose glamorous waterfall cardigans and cropped styles.

Mix and match your knitwear with key trends or keep it classic with a trusty pair of skinny jeans and a girly pair of flats. For a bit of arm candy, add a statement handbag too.
